_sText:
This is my first jailmap. It has a lot of cool stuff. 
A lot of secrets. Like a ball that wraps around your head and a gravity change. 
Enough ways to escape for T's. A lot of hidden weapons. 
CT's can go three different ways and thus can be at all spots quickly.

There are two secrets in the bigjail, one of them is easy.
Two guns and one nade in the jails, also one way to escape.
A secret to get a ball on your head and a secret to change gravity.
A secret way to go pool > soccer and a soccer > lr.
And some more.

It has a deagle trow, were the deagles are replaced with a ball. A spot for s4s. Soccer can be used for awp war. A shootout. Go in and press e while aiming at the green button. T goes left and CT goes right.  After a few secs a weapon will spawn. Time to shoot! :)

It has soccer, pool, medic, iso etc.

Try it out and comment please! :)
